data.description: Facing a charming courtyard in a secluded location with great access to all of the best of OKC. Kitchen and living have an open floor plan with a huge island - perfect for family dinners or entertaining. The kitchen is beautiful and designed as a great cooking space. Huge primary suite with giant walk in closet and beautiful en suite bath. There are 2 other large bedrooms each with its own bath, 1 is downstairs. Lots of light and great storage make this home spectacular.  2 car garage in the back. Front door opens to the courtyard. Fabulous remodeled townhouse with designer interior. This is the one you have been waiting for! Come see it today!
